  "title": "Adhoc Relief Centre Care Taker",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an <strong>Adhoc center care taker</strong> for PlayFACTO School at Tampines Central, Bedok Reservoir and Serangoon Central.</p><ul><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the premise</li><li>Prepare snacks and warm meals (no cooking required)</li><li>Provide basic care for students</li><li>Any ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Working hours are Mon-Fri, 1pm-5pm. Hourly rate of $10. Singaporeans and Singapore PRs only.<br /></p><p>Interested personnel, send your resume by applying for this role or WhatsApp to 81128546.<br /></p><p>We seek your understanding that only shortlisted candidates would be contacted.</p>",
